  "short_description": "Explore! Interact! Play minigames! Fight SCARY MONSTERS! Well... mostly scary... All while you LEARN JAPANESE?!?! Learn alphabets, collect vocab, and use what you learned to gain advantage when battling Yokai! Keep fighting until you unravel what is causing all this chaos and never give up!",
